org.intermine.bio.postprocess

Class CreateModMineMetaDataCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.intermine.bio.postprocess.CreateModMineMetaDataCache

  • public final class CreateModMineMetaDataCache
extends java.lang.Object
    Runs queries to count features, etc per submission and experiment used for display in modMine webapp. Results are written to a property file and stored in the database to be retrieved by MetaDataCache on deployment of the web application.
